Name: Ash Ketchum
Quote: That's right; I hereby declare to the Pokémon of the world... I will be the greatest Pokémon trainer... the greatest Pokémon master... of all time!

Name: Gladion
Quote: I know we aren't friends. But we aren't enemies anymore either. Keep winning. Maybe I'll see you again if you do.

Name: Goh
Quote: It's my reality, my future! And I can hold that future in the palm of my hand!

Name: Liko
Quote: We have to help Terapagos. What do you say? You ready to keep fighting?

Name: Dot
Quote: I can't run from this any longer. No, it's time I face my fears," and when she says to her Tinkaton, "Let's go, Tinkaton! Let's show them what we've got!
